551, 145.9074, 146.0651, 146.3752, 147.235, 147.3386, 146.8662, 146.9216, 147.9417, 147.5604, 148.5395, 149.5048, 149.427, 150.1654, 150.6093, 150.1048, 150.0378, 151.2254, 150.7665, 151.7419, 150.8343, 151.7391, 151.9737, 151.1922, 151.623, 153.0044, 153.072, 153.8917, 155.112, 157.1111, 156.0922, 156.761, 157.8728, 159.2294, 160.7683, 158.1144, 157.526, 157.5286, 156.6169, 158.5955, 158.1983, 158.5604, 158.1643, 158.5144, 159.1787, 159.7774, 159.4252, 159.0078, 161.1821, 162.1947, 160.8297, 159.641, 159.9818, 162.247, 162.6548, 163.215, 164.0281, 162.6609, 163.3582, 165.5541, 165.986, 165.9616, 167.4381, 167.4293, 167.8298, 167.6668, 169.8607, 165.5809, 162.6914, 164.3097, 164.3908, 163.1204, 164.2009, 163.6722, 164.4929, 165.7554, 165.5793, 165.5516, 167.2141, 167.5351, 168.4321, 169.8434, 170.2634, 167.9212, 170.5282, 169.805, 170.3535, 169.9966, 171.0811, 171.8488, 172.0924, 170.2778, 171.6077, 171.8805, 176.4122, 177.941, 176.5209, 175.0948, 175.3966, 173.1836, 177.0173, 177.8001, 176.4719, 177.2051, 175.7428], "summary_html": "<h1>商品基本面量化框架系列(二)：黄金择时因子及多周期合成</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>该研报提出了一个三维度黄金择时框架：宏观（TIPS/实际利率定价长周期收益）、中观（CFTC持仓因子增强静态多头）、微观（量价趋势度评估单品种状态）。我们将其中的因子逻辑泛化到全品种商品期货：用展期收益EMA（ryminusema252）替代TIPS作为期限结构carry因子，用席位持仓差（memberdiff20）替代CFTC持仓构造动量突破信号，用信噪比+回归斜率+自相关三指标合成趋势度因子评估品种当前趋势质量。三因子加权合成后，截面排名→连续多空信号→波动率目标缩放→定期再平衡。</p>\n<p>核心alpha来源于：(1) 展期收益EMA对期限结构信息的时序平滑使carry信号更稳定；(2) 趋势度因子帮助区分真趋势和噪声震荡，提升仓位质量；(3) 三因子组合降低了单因子的波动性。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.44</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>7.1%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.9%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-4.2%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.06</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>1759</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.35</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>2.04</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>2.18 / 0.45</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.02</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.27</span></td><td>1.78</td><td>1.14</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.5</span></td><td>1.31</td><td>1.38</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.35</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ryminusema252</code></td><td>展期收益EMA</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>memberdiff20</code></td><td>席位净持仓差</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 10 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 10 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>56</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>1758</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.4%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>46.8</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>因子1 -- 展期收益EMA carry</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{carry\\_sig}_i = 2 \\times \\text{CRank}(\\text{ryminusema252}_i) - 1</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{ryminusema252}</span> 是展期收益率的252日EMA，<span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{CRank}</span> 为截面百分位排名。</p>\n<p><strong>因子2 -- 持仓动量突破</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">z_{i,t} = \\frac{\\text{memberdiff20}_{i,t} - \\mu_{i,t}^{120}}{\\sigma_{i,t}^{120}}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal} = \\begin{cases} +1, &amp; z &gt; 0.8 \\text{ and } \\text{MA}_{20} &gt; \\text{MA}_{60} \\\\ -1, &amp; z &lt; -0.8 \\text{ and } \\text{MA}_{20} &lt; \\text{MA}_{60} \\\\ 0, &amp; \\text{otherwise} \\end{cases}</div>\n<p><strong>因子3 -- 趋势度合成</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{SNR}_w = \\frac{|P_t - P_{t-w}|}{\\sum_{i=1}^{w} |P_i - P_{i-1}|}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{NormSlope}_w = \\frac{\\hat{\\beta}_{\\text{OLS}}(P, t; w)}{\\text{std}(P; w)}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{AutoCorr}_w = \\text{rolling\\_corr}(r_t, r_{t-1}; w)</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{TQ} = \\frac{1}{3}\\sum_{c \\in \\{\\text{SNR}, \\text{NormSlope}, \\text{AutoCorr}\\}} \\text{zscore}(|c|)</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position} = \\text{sign}(\\hat{\\beta}) \\times \\min(\\text{TQ}, 3) / 3</div>\n<p><strong>合成信号</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{combo} = 0.4 \\times \\text{CRank}(\\text{carry}) + 0.2 \\times \\text{CRank}(\\text{positioning}) + 0.4 \\times \\text{CRank}(\\text{trend})</div>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>Sharpe 0.87 (combo_equal), 换手1.32, 后半段Sharpe仅0.11</td><td>初始三因子框架：ry carry + memberdiff20 z-score突破 + 趋势度(SNR/slope/autocorr)</td><td>通过backtest gate但半样本不稳定</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>换手降至0.87, 后半段升至0.27, 但2023年仍为负</td><td>添加IC gate过滤弱品种, hold从5增到10日, 降低md20阈值(1.0-&gt;0.8)并加MA方向确认, 增加carry-heavy权重和carry_trend双因子</td><td>Sharpe 1.04 (combo_eq_h10), 换手大幅降低</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>关键转折：发现ryminusema252远优于raw ry</td><td>用ryminusema252替代ry作为carry因子, 构建ryema-based combo, 测试hold=10/15/20参数网格</td><td><strong>Sharpe 1.65</strong> (combo_ryema_h10), 后半段Sharpe从0.27提升至1.11</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折</strong>: R3引入ryminusema252（展期收益率252日EMA）替代原始ry，使carry信号更平滑、更稳定。这一改变使Sharpe从1.04跃升至1.65，后半段Sharpe从0.27升至1.11，彻底解决了半样本不稳定问题。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货（约80个品种，实际有效约60个）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 每10个交易日再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>依赖数据</strong>: ryminusema252（展期收益EMA, ~37%非空）、memberdiff20（席位持仓差, ~23%非空）、OHLC（趋势度因子）</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: (1) 研报原文针对黄金单品种，泛化到全品种时部分因子(特别是CFTC持仓逻辑)在非贵金属品种上可能较弱; (2) 2023年Sharpe接近0，策略在低趋势震荡市中表现较差; (3) 与huatai_xsmom有0.67相关性，但本策略Sharpe更高(1.65 vs 1.08)</li>\n<li><strong>冗余检查</strong>: max_corr=0.67 vs huatai_xsmom_adaptive_adj (Sharpe 1.08), 本策略Sharpe更优</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.6s</li>\n</ul>"}